snippet.textDisplay: Sad part is, people actually find this entertaining.  Bunch of nick cannons, talking louder and thinking because their words were said with more decibels and authority, they must be right.  Being this unintelligent must be nice because they cant understand the intricacies of life and the worries it brings.  Classic case of the jocks versus the nerds in school.  Jocks rule through the confidence of physical strength, which represents the lower tier of society after, while the nerds play it smart and let the jocks believe they are in power. They then excel to greater heights after high school when the jocks can no longer control them and shift the power to themselves through jobs and mental effort.  I can switch out the words jocks and nerds for a bigger meaning, but if you're smart you'll understand my point, so I wont simplify it.  This is where the nerds power lies, with strenght through knowledge.
